[
  {
    "startTime": 0.266,
    "endTime": 1.401,
    "text": "Now I thought I'd share some of my favorite"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.401,
    "endTime": 3.803,
    "text": "\"weirdest Halloween ever\" stories from you guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.803,
    "endTime": 6.6,
    "text": "This first one is from @RealAmyJo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.6,
    "endTime": 9.408999999999999,
    "text": "She says, \"We rang the bell at a house, and the guy was drunk."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.409,
    "endTime": 11.440000000000001,
    "text": "He had no idea it was Halloween."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.44,
    "endTime": 12.78,
    "text": "So he just gave us each a dollar"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.78,
    "endTime": 13.812,
    "text": "and then turned off his porch light.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.813,
    "endTime": 16.449,
    "text": "[ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.449,
    "endTime": 18.818,
    "text": "\"Am I a pretty emoji?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.818,
    "endTime": 19.953000000000003,
    "text": "[ Light laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.953,
    "endTime": 21.82,
    "text": "This one's from @cam31."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.821,
    "endTime": 24.240000000000002,
    "text": "He says, \"Once at the mall, I saw five people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.24,
    "endTime": 26.259,
    "text": "walk into a public restroom dressed as Clark Kent."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.259,
    "endTime": 28.661,
    "text": "Five minutes later, all five of them came out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.661,
    "endTime": 29.362000000000002,
    "text": "dressed as Superman.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.362,
    "endTime": 32.931,
    "text": "-Yeah. -Wow, they really planned it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.8,
    "endTime": 35.568,
    "text": "\"Look, it's five birds!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.568,
    "endTime": 38.937,
    "text": "No. They could be five drones.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.938,
    "endTime": 40.54,
    "text": "[ Laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.54,
    "endTime": 41.107,
    "text": "Just update."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.107,
    "endTime": 43.43,
    "text": "Yeah, update. Just trying to make it modern."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.43,
    "endTime": 44.811,
    "text": "\"I'm gonna call an Uber.\" You're making it modern."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.811,
    "endTime": 46.913,
    "text": "Yeah, making Superman modern."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.913,
    "endTime": 48.58,
    "text": "This one's from @NatalieWild7."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.581,
    "endTime": 51.785000000000004,
    "text": "She says, \"My friend and I were walking through a haunted house"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.785,
    "endTime": 52.452,
    "text": "when a clown jumped out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.452,
    "endTime": 55.321,
    "text": "My friend freaked out and screamed, 'Not today, biatch,'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.321,
    "endTime": 56.723,
    "text": "and then ran away.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.723,
    "endTime": 59.559,
    "text": "[ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.559,
    "endTime": 61.494,
    "text": "Why go?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.494,
    "endTime": 63.263,
    "text": "Stay in your lane, clown."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.263,
    "endTime": 64.998,
    "text": "[ Laughter ] Unh-unh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.998,
    "endTime": 67.56700000000001,
    "text": "This one's from @GumGummerson."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.567,
    "endTime": 69.735,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.736,
    "endTime": 71.171,
    "text": "Ol' Gum Gummerson!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.171,
    "endTime": 74.7,
    "text": "-Old Gum Gummerson. -I've been here many years."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.7,
    "endTime": 77.277,
    "text": "I got my prospectin' pan. -Old Gum Gummerson."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.277,
    "endTime": 81.44800000000001,
    "text": "Man, get out of here, you -- -Dagnabbit!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.448,
    "endTime": 82.148,
    "text": "What's Gum say?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.148,
    "endTime": 85.417,
    "text": "Gum says, \"A trick-or-treater once showed up at my door"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.418,
    "endTime": 88.15400000000001,
    "text": "in a poncho that had the name John written on it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.154,
    "endTime": 91.124,
    "text": "When we asked what he was, he replied, 'I'm John.'\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.124,
    "endTime": 92.759,
    "text": "[ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.759,
    "endTime": 93.993,
    "text": "Good costume. -Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.993,
    "endTime": 96.161,
    "text": "Then Gum gave him some gum."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.162,
    "endTime": 98.631,
    "text": "This one's from @MissLoriT."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.631,
    "endTime": 100.767,
    "text": "-Oh, @MrsLoriT. -Oh, Mrs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.767,
    "endTime": 102.735,
    "text": "Maybe she's married to Mr. T."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.735,
    "endTime": 103.369,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.369,
    "endTime": 104.804,
    "text": "-She says -- -I pity the fool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.804,
    "endTime": 106.84,
    "text": "-What's that? -I pity the fool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.84,
    "endTime": 110.176,
    "text": "[ Laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.978,
    "endTime": 112.711,
    "text": "Who's married to Mr. T."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.712,
    "endTime": 115.181,
    "text": "The idea was that Superman used to say, \"It's a bird.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.181,
    "endTime": 116.349,
    "text": "\"It's a plane. It's Superman.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.349,
    "endTime": 117.717,
    "text": "He didn't say it. The people would say that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.717,
    "endTime": 120.453,
    "text": "No, humans walking around Metropolis."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.453,
    "endTime": 121.321,
    "text": "Right, would go, \"Oh, my gosh,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.321,
    "endTime": 122.956,
    "text": "it's a bird, it's a plane, it's Superman."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.956,
    "endTime": 125.291,
    "text": "Oh, it's a plane. No, it's Superman.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.291,
    "endTime": 127.6,
    "text": "Now you're saying, \"Is that a drone?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.6,
    "endTime": 130.53,
    "text": "That's correct, or is that a -- some type of --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.53,
    "endTime": 132.65,
    "text": "-Person. -A flying --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.65,
    "endTime": 134.501,
    "text": "A remote-control flying thing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.501,
    "endTime": 137.70000000000002,
    "text": "Is that some sort of a flying device?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.7,
    "endTime": 138.905,
    "text": "Maybe Balloon Boy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.905,
    "endTime": 145.411,
    "text": "And so people say, \"Is that a drone or Balloon Boy?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.411,
    "endTime": 146.346,
    "text": "No, by golly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.346,
    "endTime": 149.68200000000002,
    "text": "-It's just Superman. -In fact, it's just Superman."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.682,
    "endTime": 151.81699999999998,
    "text": "Yet again I was tricked."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.818,
    "endTime": 156.89000000000001,
    "text": "-You fooled me once again. -You fooled me once again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.89,
    "endTime": 157.58999999999997,
    "text": "[ Laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.59,
    "endTime": 159.792,
    "text": "Kryptoday and Kryptonite."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.792,
    "endTime": 162.428,
    "text": "[ Laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.997,
    "endTime": 166.16600000000003,
    "text": "Oh, my God."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.834,
    "endTime": 171.337,
    "text": "Whaa! Shwack. Trick or treat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.337,
    "endTime": 173.90599999999998,
    "text": "This one's from @PunkReckless. -Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.907,
    "endTime": 178.711,
    "text": "She says, \"I was dressed as a fortune teller at a party."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.711,
    "endTime": 179.71200000000002,
    "text": "A guy asked me to read his palm,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.712,
    "endTime": 182.48,
    "text": "so I told him he'd get drunk and have a good time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.48,
    "endTime": 185.25099999999998,
    "text": "He came back an hour later, told me I was the real deal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.251,
    "endTime": 186.92000000000002,
    "text": "Then he fell over a table.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.92,
    "endTime": 189.655,
    "text": "[ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.724,
    "endTime": 194.393,
    "text": "This last one is from @MattLong1."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.394,
    "endTime": 196.796,
    "text": "He says, \"I once got so drunk at a Halloween party"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.796,
    "endTime": 199.265,
    "text": "that when I got home, I egged my own house.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.265,
    "endTime": 200.13199999999998,
    "text": "There you have it, everybody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.133,
    "endTime": 201.834,
    "text": "Those are \"Tonight Show Hashtags.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.834,
    "endTime": 203.303,
    "text": "To check out more of our favorites,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.303,
    "endTime": 206.739,
    "text": "go to tonightshow.com/hashtags."
  }
]